<h2>Async load CSS</h2>
<li><a href="https://github.com/n0mad01/asyncLoader">asyncLoader</a> - async script/stylesheet loader</li>
<li><a href="http://addyosmani.github.io/basket.js/">basket.js</a> - async script/resource loader with support for localStorage caching. Can be <a href="https://github.com/andrewwakeling/basket-css-example">extended</a><a data-role="trackawesomelist-badge" href="https://github.com/andrewwakeling/basket-css-example" style="text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;"><span style="color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;"><span style="padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;">stars</span><span style="padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;">19</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{"type":"repo","stargazerCount":19,"repo":"andrewwakeling/basket-css-example"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> to load stylesheets.</li>
